happy valentine’s day my lovees i’m sorry papas not home  it’s -20 in canada today. working outside with my cast and crew of SEE 2. just want to send my aloha to everyone i’m thankful for all of you  we are making art. in the fucking COLD but we are doing what we love  @thefrozenfewofficial  photo @kurpius. aloha papa.  see u soon

I AM HONOURED TO BE IN THIS CREW @thefrozenfewofficial  @stockezy you killed it  looking forward to all the amazing moments captured by our amazing photographers.  @leicacamerausa. aloha j

hands down one of the greatest weekends i’ve ever had. mad crazy love to @leicacamerausa we shot on all the cameras the new SL2 m10 monochrome my favourite M10 ASC check it out it’s next level.  and @reddigitalcinema let us test out the new komodo 3lbs 6k blew my mind and always @leitzcine lenses. i am so blessed to be filming with this team  big mahalo’s to @yeoleghost  for creating the world all the @thefrozenfewofficial who have accepted me in. @sushi_thefreewheeler for the amazing present  all our photographers and DPS  and most of all to @guinnessus and @mananalu.water for the hydration😜. special mahalo to @carhartt @holdfastgear for my rig. @stockezy @odeumfilms.tv @_ohhhsnap @sumnerdilworth @deanchoochlandry @kurpius @i.am.aurelius @da_bray chrissy laura @bluetodd @jj_tribe  sorry if i forgot anyone you killed it.  love to all my new friends  i am blessed.  aloha j

this was just warming up the bikes i don’t want to ruin the surprises but this weekend was one of the greatest shoots i have ever done. working with @harleydavidson directing my next commercial with an army of shooters and riders  new bikes old bikes. on ice in the heat  desert and jungle. this is just the beginning i wish i could show everything but for now. just trust me. i am beyond stoked and proud.  all my aloha to the frozen few. @thefrozenfewofficial i met the most amazing men this weekend truly friends for life.  i love my job.  mahalo to @leicacamerausa @leitzcine @reddigitalcinema @jj_tribe  for always supporting me and backing me up. @harleydavidson your gonna be proud  @sushi_thefreewheeler i’m so honoured to receive your gift 88 crazy eights uniform i will forever wear it with pride @yeoleghost none of this would have been possible without you what a wonderful world u have created love u mel.  many more thanks to come  aloha j
